quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,"Si a ∆īawii ka laana an e …ďen wonndu…ďe e maa…óa immorde e gom…óin…ďe da…óu…ďe …ďen, haray maaku: "Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, On danndu…óo en immorde e yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďen O halki …ďe."
  23,29,"Maaku: "Joom am, jippinam ka leydi jippinngol barkinaangol, ko An woni Mo∆ī∆īo jippinoowo"."
  23,30,"Pellet, no e nder …óum ko jaŇčtaa …óoo immorde e danndugol Nuuhu e gom…óin…ďe …ďen wonndude e makko, e halkeede yeddu…ďe …ďen; daliilaaji fee√Īu…ói e dow kattan…óe Amen fii wallugol Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen e halkungol fennu…ďe …ďe …ďen, fii kala Men wonii ko Men jarribor…ďe yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen Nulugol mo faade e ma…ď…ďe fii yo …ďanngu hakkunde gom…óin…óo on e keefeero on maa…óum …óoftii…óo on e geddo on."
  23,31,"Refti Men fu…ó…ói …ďaawo halkeede yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen mofte goo."
  23,32,"Men Nuli e ma…ď…ďe Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe himo nodda…ďe ka Alla, o maakani …ďe: "Rewee Alla Kanko tun alanaa on rewetee…óo e Goonga tanaa Makko O Senike. Enee, kaa on hulirtaa Alla wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin e jokkugol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin?!""
  23,33,"Koohoo…ďe teddu…ďe …ďen ka yim…ďe makko yeddu…ďe Alla, …ďe fenni Laakara on e ko woni ton kon immorde mbarjaari e Lepte, ko Men yaajinani …ďe kon immorde e neemaaji ka ngurdan aduna bewini …ďe. ∆Āe wi'ani jokku…ďe …ďe …ďen e puy…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen- : "Oo wonaali si wanaa …ďanndunke yeru moo…óon himo √Īaama ko √Īaamoton kon, himo yara ko yaroton kon, o maraa ko senndi mo e moo…óon haa tawa o imminee Nulaa…óo faade e moo…óon"."
  23,34,"Mi woondii si on …óoftike …ďanndinke wano mo'on, pellet, ontuma haray onon ko on hayru…ďe sabu waasude nafitorgol mo'on …óoftagol mo sabu …óalugol moo…óon sanamuuji mon …óin, e jokkugol on mo …ďural alanaa …óum e dow moo…óon."
  23,35,"Enee, oo aa∆īii…óo wonnde ko o Nulaa…óo, o fodu on wonnde si on maayii on wontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e ki…ó…óe wonndema onon on yaltinoyte ka genaale moo…óon hara ko on wuuru…ďe?! mbela …óum ko hakkille ?!"
  23,36,"No wo…ó…ói haa fanti kon ko foda…óon …óum immorde e yaltinegol ka genaali moo…óon hara ko on wuuru…ďe …ďaawo mayde moo…óon, e wontugol moo…óon mbullaari e ∆īi'e ki…ó…óe."
  23,37,"Ngurdam …óam wonaali si wanaa ngurdam aduna …óam, wanah ngurdam Laakara, wuuru…ďe …ďen e amen no maay hara …ďe wuuritataa, wo…ď…ďe goo kadi jibinee …ďe wuura, men wonaali yaltinoytee…ďe …ďaawo mayde amen nden fii hasboore √Ďalnde darngal."
  23,38,"Oo won…óo nodditaade wonndema ko o Nulaa…óo faade e moo…óon o wonaali si wonaa gorko fefindii-…óo fawi e Alla sabu ngol nodditagol makko, men wonaali gom…óinoo…ďe mo."
  23,39,"Nulaa…óo on maaki: "Joomam, wallam e hoore ma…ď…ďe …óum woni yo…ďtano…óaa lam e ma…ď…ďe sabu ko …ďe finni lam kon"."
  23,40,"Alla jaabori mo Daalugol: "∆Āaawo jamaanu fan…óu…óo aray …ďee fennu…ďe ko addu…óaa kon wonta nimsu…ďe e dow ko …ďe wonnoo fennude kon"."
  23,41,"Hito sa…ótungo halkayngo nanngi …ďe sabu hanndu- gol ma…ď…ďe e Lepte …óen e sanndal…óaagu ma…ď…ďe, …óe wattini …ďe halkii…ďe yeru duu√Īo ilol ngol, halakuyee wonanii yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,42,"Refti …ďaawo halkeede ma…ď…ďe Men fu…ó…ói yim…ďe e moftaaji goo wano yim…ďe Luutu, e yim…ďe Su'aybu, e yim…ďe Yuunusa."